summary.description:
Distributed API-service that connects a database of unicorns
                with ChatGPT and Spotify to generate a fable with a paired music track from 
                Spotify. A Unicorn contains data like name, description, finder and location.
                This together with "happy" or "scary" input gets us the fable, while the name of the
                unicorn generates the song.

                The fable is shown in the web application and all of the input comes from here.
